 May through October and continues every second Wednesday from November through April. Go to www.WildFlightFarm.ca to subscribe to an email newsletter with regular updates on market vendors.',1,'2013-07-29 18:02:18','2013-09-16 00:35:58',13,'Location',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Salmon Arm','CA','Canada','BC','British Columbia'),(488,50.4475,-119.198,NULL,'3371 Pleasant Valley Road, Armstrong, V0E 1B0, BC','Armstrong Farmers\' Market','','Thompson-Okanagan','250-546-1986','http://met.bcfarmersmarket.org/market/armstrong-farmers-market','','','Saturdays, Summer: Established in 1973, we believe our market is the oldest in BC. In true country atmosphere you can get a coffee and a muffin, a smokie in a bun, ethnic foods, conventional and organic vegetables and fruits, homemade bread and other baked goods, jams and jellies, cheeses, sausage, free range eggs, snacks, gorgeous flower arrangements, plants, home and garden accessories, beautiful wooden bowls, jewelry boxes, wooden planters and garden furniture, unique clothing for kids and adults, fabulous hand made jewelry, fashion accessories, soaps and body products, and numerous other items produced by the vendors. Our motto is \"we make it, bake it or grow it\". It\'s a great way to spend a Saturday morning. As you stroll along making your purchases you can visit with friends and neighbours while being entertained by some of our local musicians. See you there!',1,'2013-07-29 18:02:19','2013-07-29 18:02:19',13,'Location',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(489,51.183,-120.123,NULL,'4614 Barriere Town Road, Barriere, V0E 1E0, BC','Barriere Farmers\' Market','','Thompson-Okanagan','250-672-5159','http://met.bcfarmersmarket.org/market/barriere-farmers-market','','','Thursdays, Summer: Come check out the home made goodies and home grown fruits and veggies at the Barriere Farmers\' Market. Beef, pork and lamb from 4 bar S ranch and free range eggs from Watersmeet Farm. Cedar garden furniture and paintings by local artists